  "title": "Landscape Coordinator/Landscape Manager Assistance",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Attend site visits and tender show round</li>\n  <li>Propose and design simple yet sustainable landscape designs for specified sites</li>\n  <li>Prepare quotes and landscape maintenance reports</li>\n  <li>Coordinate work orders with ground crew</li>\n  <li>Dealing with complaints from client on site</li>\n  <li>Prepare maintenance schedule</li>\n  <li>Monitor and recording of site staff attendance</li>\n  <li>Handling few projects assigned and coordination</li>\n  <li>To be responsible for the administrative and operational for landscape project aspects, including liaise with customers for project requirements and progress</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree/Diploma in Horticulture, Arboriculture or other related fields with minimum of 1 yr experience in landscaping industries</li>\n  <li>Required language(s): English, Chinese (in order to deal with complaints from Chinese speaking client on site)</li>\n  <li>Dynamic and energetic</li>\n  <li>Good team player with ability to lead and multi-task</li>\n  <li>Committed to work</li>\n  <li>Required Skill(s): Microsoft Office</li>\n  <li>Excellent interpersonal and communication skills</li>\n  <li>Prefer candidates with horticulture or arborist knowledge</li>\n  <li>On-the-job training provided</li>\n  <li>Entry level candidates with the revelant Polytechnic / WSQ Diploma / Degree are welcomed</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Working Hours and Office Location:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>5.5-day work week</li>\n  <li>Office location: Mandai Estate</li>\n  <li>Work location: Various Sites</li>\n</ul>",
